    "Consequently, these keywords represent key trending topics in AI for diagnosis and treatment of breast cancer and its patients.",
    "The impact of AI technologies on clinical outcomes is multifaceted, encompassing improved diagnostic accuracy, reduced workload for radiologists, enhanced visualization, and the potential for personalized medicine.",
    "These advancements can lead to earlier detection and more effective treatment of breast cancer, ultimately improving patient care and outcomes.]",
    "The \"Make in India\" initiative has led to AI advancements like Telerad Tech's \"MammoAssist\" and Niramai Health's affordable, non-invasive screening tool, both enhancing early breast cancer detection and radiologist efficiency.",
    "Regenerative AI, continuously improving with new data, supports reliable diagnostics across populations."
